metadata.name: Looking at the
metadata.description:
appeared in the hands of the founder, the silver knights beside the sword cried out at once. Instead, it was the black robe staring at the eyes of all this, suddenly felt as if there was something wrong...



"Wait, this is not right, be careful --!!"



Before the black robe's voice fell, fang Zheng, who had been half kneeling on the ground, sprang up suddenly. He grasped his sword with both hands, raised it high, and waved it forward forcefully. The next moment, I saw the sword Pierce the silver knight's body without any appearance.
